DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates how to create a rollup (hierarchical continuous aggregate) using the `@Rollup` and `@RollupColumn` decorators. It aggregates hourly statistics from the `HourlyPageViews` continuous aggregate into daily summaries.
