TITLE: Create Continuous Aggregate with TypeORM
DESCRIPTION: This TypeScript code defines a continuous aggregate `DailyEnergyStats` for the `EnergyMetric` hypertable using TypeORM. It calculates daily energy statistics such as total consumption, total generation, peak consumption, and average temperature. The refresh policy is set to start 2 days in the past, end 1 hour in the past, and refresh every hour.
