TITLE: Custom SQL Generation with @timescaledb/core in Typescript
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates custom SQL generation using @timescaledb/core. It shows how to generate hypertable creation SQL and compression statistics SQL separately.
SOURCE: https://github.com/timescale/timescaledb-ts/blob/main/packages/core/README.md#_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
const hypertable = TimescaleDB.createHypertable('measurements', {
  by_range: { column_name: 'time' },
});

// Generate only the hypertable creation SQL
const createSql = hypertable.up().build();

// Generate only the compression SQL
const compressionSql = hypertable
  .compression()
  .stats({ select: { total_chunks: true } })
  .build();
```

